    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/cec98be3d066c317e5e9aab75efd70f6.poster.avif?t=1728859137\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/cec98be3d066c317e5e9aab75efd70f6.webm?t=1728859137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/cec98be3d066c317e5e9aab75efd70f6.mp4?t=1728859137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>沈浸于这款拥有美丽 3D 环境的迷人解迷冒险游戏中。进入一座壮观且古老的城堡中探索充满其中的秘密仓库与密室。解开复杂的谜题、找到遗失的宝藏并揭开科学与魔法的秘密。<br> <br> 在一个遥远的小岛上有着一座历经风雨的古老城堡。多年来，它宁静的矗立在那。而村民们却仍然记得那些有关噩梦、风暴与在雾中诡异光亮的老故事。最近，一个神秘的无线电信号开始从城堡里广播出来。城堡里有东西苏醒了，且必须有人去一探究竟。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/b7a1e452520a961ee4ebf7179cd84a53.poster.avif?t=1728859137\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/b7a1e452520a961ee4ebf7179cd84a53.webm?t=1728859137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/b7a1e452520a961ee4ebf7179cd84a53.mp4?t=1728859137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏主特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>无数的秘密供您探索</strong><br>一路解开一道道复杂的谜题来解锁城堡的最终秘密或者选择您自己的道路：寻找秘密仓库或是秘密走道、找到所有的失落宝藏并探索城堡与其前任住户的历史。<br><br></li><li><strong>写实的环境与生动的故事</strong><br>在精致细节、写实环境的世界中投身于一则有趣的故事。探索遗弃的房间、寻找散落的书信并找回被遗忘的纪念品来拼凑出那些城堡以往住户们的故事。<br><br></li><li><strong>活络的玩法</strong><br>操控复杂的机制、解开精致的谜题并以活络、写实的方式与环境直接互动。<br><br></li><li><strong>极为简单的界面</strong><br>以简约、简易的界面来探索城堡的秘密，同时您只要轻松的一点，便能够完全隐藏此界面。</li></ul><br>《天坛之眼》是一款注重探索、解谜与发现的游戏。您会相信围绕着这座城堡的故事与传说，还是会壮起胆子并以客观、好奇的角度自己找出事实？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/48e2062aeaab6e023368f8d157b17329.poster.avif?t=1728859137\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/48e2062aeaab6e023368f8d157b17329.webm?t=1728859137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454250/extras/48e2062aeaab6e023368f8d157b17329.mp4?t=1728859137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
